POSSIBLE ANSWERS:
(B): 13.0
Dog:9-3=6 lives
Mouse:6+7=13 lives
#### 13
(A): 19.0
Cat has 9 lives
Dog has 3 more than cat: 9 + 3 = 12 lives
Mouse has 7 more than dog: 12 + 7 = 19 lives
#### 19
